article.headline: Cal St-Fullerton 85, Louisiana-Lafayette 49
article.story: FULLERTON, Calif. (AP) -- Justin Burns scored 16 points and Bobby Brown added 11 points and 10 assists as Cal State Fullerton defeated Louisiana-Lafayette 85-49 Wednesday. Frank Robinson scored 13 points for the Titans (8-2), and Marcus Crenshaw added 12 on 4-of-7 3-point shooting. Scott Cutley added seven points and a game-high seven rebounds. Ross Mouton scored 19 points to lead Louisiana-Lafayette (2-9).
